metadata.name: Invocation - I
metadata.description:
Studio on Abstraction is my genesis collection available on Foundation and is an exercise-like collection on abstract and divergent thinking. A collection that invokes the unknown, the geometric, the color, the texture. Part of my creative process is mixing tools. Here the code is also part.


Digital abstract.
